好的，以下是移除send按钮，并且在输入框中按下回车键时执行sendMessage方法的修改后的代码：

```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Chat App</title>
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .chat {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .chat-history {
        height: 300px;
        overflow-y: scroll;
      }

      .message {
        margin: 10px 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .message-left {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }

      .message-right {
        justify-content: flex-end;
      }

      .message-text {
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #e6e6e6;
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .message-left .message-text {
        margin-left: 10px;
      }

      .message-right .message-text {
        margin-right: 10px;
      }

      .chat-input {
        margin-top: 20px;
        display: flex;
      }

      .chat-input input {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: none;
      }

      .chat-input button {
        display: none;
      }
    </style>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/vue@next"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
          <h1>Chat App</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="chat">
          <div class="chat-history" ref="chatHistory">
            <div class="message" v-for="(message, index) in messages" :key="index" :class="{ 'message-left': message.role === 'a', 'message-right': message.role === 'b' }">
              <div class="message-text">{{ message.content }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chat-input">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Type your message" v-model="newMessage" @keyup.enter="sendMessage">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script>
      const app = Vue.createApp({
        data() {
          return {
            messages: [
              { role: 'a', content: 'Hello' },
              { role: 'b', content: 'How are you?' },
              { role: 'a', content: 'I\'m fine. Thanks.' }
            ],
            newMessage: ''
          }
        },
        methods: {
          sendMessage() {
            if (this.newMessage) {
              this.messages.push({ role: 'b', content: this.newMessage });
              this.newMessage = '';
              // 将滚动条滚动到最新消息的位置
              this.$nextTick(() => {
                this.$refs.chatHistory.scrollTop = this.$refs.chatHistory.scrollHeight;
              });
            }
          }
        }
      });

      app.mount('#app');
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
```

在这个示例中，我们将send按钮的CSS样式设置为了"display: none"，移除了按钮的显示。同时，我们在输入框中添加了"@keyup.enter"事件监听，在输入框中按下回车键时执行sendMessage方法。
